  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>Cut your <strong>broccoli</strong> into small florets</p><p>Cut the <strong>broccoli stem[s]</strong> into bite-sized pieces</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1680536252847-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1680536252847-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1680536252847-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1680536252847-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1680536252847-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and cut your <strong>brown onion[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>into quarters, then separate the wedges so you end up with a pile of onion petals</p><p>Top, tail, peel and chop your<strong> carrot[s]</strong> into batons</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1-1680536256496-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1-1680536256496-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1-1680536256496-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1-1680536256496-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1-1680536256496-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>broccoli florets</strong>, <strong>carrot batons</strong>, <strong>broccoli stems</strong>, <strong>onion petals</strong> and a very generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for an initial 3-4 min or until the veg is starting to soften</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1-1680536260022-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1-1680536260022-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1-1680536260022-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1-1680536260022-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1-1680536260022-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the veg is cooking, peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>cornflour</strong> in a bowl with your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>hoisin sauce</strong> and 150ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [200ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[250ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>hoisin mixture</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1-1680536263084-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1-1680536263084-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1-1680536263084-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
